cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and defending against model extraction attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses security and privacy concerns, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The experiments involve image and speech data, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), respectively. Finally, the paper involves training and optimizing models, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
